    <div data-cid="4738264">
        <div class="main review-item" id="4738264">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/crazydoctor/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img9.doubanio.com/icon/u3776955-5.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/crazydoctor/" class="name">吸引陨石</a>

            <span class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>

        <span content="2011-03-03" class="main-meta">2011-03-03 14:43:19</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4738264/">对不起，我想说这书挺烂的</a></h2>

                <div id="review_4738264_short" class="review-short" data-rid="4738264">
                    <div class="short-content">

                               这完全是一套玄幻小说。     看的第一部盗墓类的小说相信和很多人一样是《鬼吹灯》，虽然完结的有些让人不爽，但总体来说是有个完满的交代——我是个业余的阅读者，专业意见完全提不出。     后来发现又跳出本《盗墓笔记》，必须承认第一本还是满吸引人的，估计“三叔”...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4738264-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_4738264_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_4738264_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="4738264" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-4738264">
                                11
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="4738264" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-4738264">
